                <note rend="inline" type="source">493.11/2112: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-03-17T19:00:00-05:00"
                            >March 17, 1938—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>82. Your 175, March 16, 5 p.m., in regard to the Fan Biological Institute at
                    Peiping. The Department perceives no objection to your taking, orally and
                    informally, the action suggested.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
